// Planar Sphere
@0 = ~Oh, such an extraordinary place! A gift for any talented mage! (Like me...)~
@1 = ~And this Valygar refused it! He would prefer death to discovering his true potential!~
@2 = ~You, mages, are all the same - vain and arrogant. You are thinking only about gaining more power. That is why your kind is despised.~
@3 = ~And who is loving you, baboon? Your animal friends? Only they will mourn your demise. But great wizards remain in history forever.~
@4 = ~I have no interest in your opinions. I have my way and I'm not going to change it.~
@5 = ~You are just a fool.~